room_title: Escape room "DEA Bust" by Escape Strategy in Tampa
room_address: 1312 Apollo Beach Blvd, Apollo Beach, FL 33572
room_description: You have recently been promoted to detective in the DEA. Your boss has given you a seemingly impossible task: investigate and take down the biggest drug cartel of Miami. You have found one of their known safe houses, but you must enter and leave without the drug lords noticing if you wish to avoid tipping them off. Can you find the evidence and escape before the dealers return?
